  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigating the perioperative effect of moxonidine. In a randomized double-blind fashion,
      patients undergoing vascular surgery will receive moxonidine 0.2 mg or placebo from the day
      before surgery until day 4 after surgery. Holter-EKG for 48 h, starting just before surgery.
      Repeated 12-lead EKG, measurements of Troponin I and BNP, clinical visitations, follow-up
      interviews at 6 and 12 months
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
